[Result "*"]

1. c4 c5 { +=4 } 2. Nf3 g6
{ This is the big alternative with the idea to play for d2-d4 very soon, most often right on move 3 or 4.  Or }
3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nc6 5. e4
{ , which transposes to the Accelerated Dragon Maroczy Bind. A good opening for White, but quite complex theory necessary. }
