{ Black opens up the centre. This is a very ambitious and interesting line. }
4. cxd5 Nxd5 5. Nc3 Nc7
{ Clearly the best option. Black keeps the Knight and intends to increase his central presence with ...e5 for a reversed Maroczy bind. }
6. Nf3
{ This is my main recommendation, but I like to point out an interesting alternative in Qa4+. }
