{ This is a very sound setup for Black. White won't get much against it. } 5.
cxd5 { This is the most direct move. } 5... Bxf3
{ This is the best move I think. } 6. Bxf3 cxd5 7. O-O Nc6 8. Nc3 Nf6 { +=4 }
