{ This looks a bit crazy at first, but is not that bad ! } 9. h4 Qd4 10. Nf3
{ Of course White could play just like in the main line, but I think the insertion of h5 and h4 rather helps Black, so I looked for an alternative. }
10... Qe4 11. Qd1
{ This is a completely new position. White will sac a pawn with b3 and get good compensation. }
