{ Unsurprisingly, we go 2 g3 again. } 2... d5 3. Bg2 Nf6 4. Nf3 Be7 5. O-O O-O
{ +=4 } 6. d4
{ leads to a main line Catalan and is a serious option to expand your repertoire with. }
*

