7... Be7 { is the most frequently played move actually. } 8. dxc5 Bxc5 9. a3
O-O 10. b4 Be7 11. Bb2 Bf6 12. Qb3
{ is something already looked at above. White has more space, a great Bishop on g2 and easy moves to make  (Rd1 etc)  . The Semi Tarrasch without Nc3 being played is just a good line for White. }
