1. c4 e6 2. g3 d5 3. Bg2 { The most frequently played move is the natural }
3... d4
{ Black takes more space in the centre. White now will get a Benoni with 1-2 extra tempi - one for being White, one for Black most likely needing e6-e5, losing an additional tempo. I am not a huge fan of playing a Reversed Benoni, but 2 tempi are really nice for White. }
4. Nf3 Nc6 5. O-O Nf6 6. d3 Be7 { +=4 } 7. e3 { is also fine. } *

