{ Black has to react now. If White just gets h4-h5 in his attack will become irresistable. }
8... h5 { That's better than ....h6, but still not a walk in the park. } 9. Qd2
Re8 10. g4 { A very nice idea to remember ! } 10... hxg4 11. h5 Nc6 12. hxg6
fxg6 13. Bh6 *

